# Keep host build artifacts out of image build contexts. Critically, never copy host node_modules
# (Windows symlinks/junctions break Linux module resolution) or per-service Python .venvs.
**/node_modules
**/.venv
**/dist
**/build
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
**/.pytest_cache
**/.mypy_cache
**/.ruff_cache
**/.turbo
.git
.github
*.db
_demo_exports
datasets
models
**/.DS_Store
